  "rationale": "<p>Choice A is correct. Adding the like terms on the left-hand side of the given equation yields <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"5 times, open parenthesis, x minus 5, close parenthesis, equals 10\"></span>. Dividing both sides of this equation by 5 yields <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x minus 5, equals 2\"></span>.<p>Choice B is incorrect and may result from subtracting 5, not dividing by 5, on both sides of the equation <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"5 times, open parenthesis, x minus 5, close parenthesis, equals 10\"></span>. Choice C is incorrect. This is the value of <span class=\"italic\">x</span>, not the value of <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x minus 5\"></span>. Choice D is incorrect. This is the value of <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x plus 5\"></span>, not the value of <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x minus 5\"></span>.</p></p>\n",
